plays.text: Jumpball. Jarron Collins vs. Adonal Foyle. Danny Fortson gains possession.
Jason Richardson made 6 ft Two Point Shot. Assisted by Gilbert Arenas.
John Stockton made Layup. Assisted by Bryon Russell.
Jarron Collins made 4 ft Two Point Shot. Assisted by John Stockton.
Jarron Collins missed Free Throw 1 of 1.
Jarron Collins missed 5 ft Jumper. Blocked by Adonal Foyle.
Karl Malone made 5 ft Hook Shot.
Karl Malone missed Free Throw 1 of 1.
Antawn Jamison made 4 ft Two Point Shot. Assisted by Gilbert Arenas.
Karl Malone made 11 ft Two Point Shot. Assisted by Bryon Russell.
Antawn Jamison made 7 ft Two Point Shot. Assisted by Gilbert Arenas.
Bryon Russell missed 4 ft Jumper. Blocked by Adonal Foyle.
Jarron Collins made Layup. Assisted by John Stockton.
Adonal Foyle made Free Throw 1 of 2.
Larry Hughes enters the game for Jason Richardson.
